title: Sports Briefing | Hockey: Babcock Wins First as Leafs’ Coach
text: Babcock Wins First as Leafs’ Coach By THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   Leo Komarov scored two late goals, and Toronto beat the host Columbus Blue Jackets , 6-3, to give Mike Babcock his first victory as coach of the Maple Leafs. ■ Joe Pavelski and Brent Burns scored in the shootout and the San Jose Sharks posted a 2-1 victory over the Devils in Newark.
